Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:21.66,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A strong heart reinforces reasoning power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:23.14,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The steady rhythm reveals the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:24.79,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The client is a beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:26.92,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A strange request leads to a case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:28.29,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Perceiving the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:29.92,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:32.09,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name is: Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:47.04,Title,Sign,0,0,0,,THE CLIENT FULL OF LIES\N(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're looking for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:57.01,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes, I really must see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm a little tied up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anything that can be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I'm actually near your office already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:09.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's OK, I'd like to at least talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:11.81,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:13.02,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Lightning has come flying through!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:14.69,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The winner is Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:17.95,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}With that amazing come-from-behind\Nvictory, the final race is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lost again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:20.87,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:21.99,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mouri{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:23.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I just say I was busy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I mean, discussing it would be just fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do your work already...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what kind of person called just then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was some older woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said she's coming over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'll be like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Please help me find my long lost first love!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'll definitely be like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Ikenami, who just called a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize for intruding on you so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:20.84,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Ikenami Shizuka\NClient
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:21.26,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,My friend claimed that if I asked Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nfor help, we could find him easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I very much so hope you'll help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, come sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She's such a beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:32.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did Dad go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies for having you wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:41.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madamosielle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was busy reviewing some elementary murder case files.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, please have a seat on the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps we may rest your heart before discussing this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about some drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:04.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's begun again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're looking for a classmate from middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were both involved in kendo as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't there be an address in the yearbook?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he moved before graduation, the\Ninformation supplied for him was minimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:29.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a photograph from back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:35.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for the one in the center holding the gold cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Shibata Shirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this cute girl next to him be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that would be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This photograph is already thirty years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Thirty years old!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means you're over forty years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I turn forty-two this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:59.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, since this photograph was taken\Nwhen he was in the seventh grade...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably a bit taller now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I get a list of hobbies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:06.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, he likes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:09.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:14.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really liked knitting, so I make a lot of sweaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a perfect hobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mother likes to knit as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you're probably a great cook as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not good at it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I ended up doing this while trying last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, what does that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Women with weaknesses are more attractive anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:42.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right! Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like Mom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I really have a lot of weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's probably why I'm still single at this age.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:54.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're single!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:06:00.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe men haven't noticed\Nsuch a beautiful and honorable woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must all be blind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just like the person who split from\Nmy mother, what were they thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:22.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, my throat just isn't well right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm allergic to dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just cleaning, so there's dust everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, we can go elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for being troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason you want to find this\NShibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is to ask for that photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:53.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The photograph was taken when we were\Nin eighth grade, on the summer fair day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just a picture of me holding\Nthe championship plaque.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My grandmother accidentally threw\Nthe award away a few days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I thought about it and was reminded of that photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why does Shibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} have the photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was using it as a bookmark while reading a\Nbook I borrowed from him and forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time I realized it, he was already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:17.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't want to find him because he's your first love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any other information?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iced lemon tea for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:36.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Reiko"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just what he used to call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:53.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used to say there was a character named Reiko in the\Nbook he let me borrow that had a personality like mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what will you have, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iced coffee for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This definitely isn't enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With only his name, age, and a thirty\Nyear old photograph to go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I should have used that person's brilliant mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard others mention him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That high school detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say Kudo Shinichi comes and\Ngoes from your detective agency often.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, that brat won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He only gives us a stupid call every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I didn't know they were so stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:47.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:50.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What if this was noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:54.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}By them already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:59.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could they have already deduced this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:08.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you about to say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the point in asking this brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:15.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But sometimes he notices interesting\Nthings that no one else does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since this guy is holding the cup,\Nhe must have got first place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was already this good in seventh grade...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have attended some sort of recorded\Ncompetition at some point, even if he had problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a person who participated named Shibata Shirou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say he always participates and is usually in the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now, he's a physical education\Nteacher at Shizouka High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:05.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He lives together with his wife at an apartment building.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go call for a rent-a-car now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great that we've found him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Found him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:19.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We've already found who she was looking for, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:22.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What confuses me is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:25.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This woman full of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:29.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She lied about everything she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:32.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just what does she want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:35.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could she be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hiding her identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, hey, or could she be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could this woman be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to you, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess no one's in...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it's Sunday, they may have gone out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's head out and come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:18.03,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Yoshikawa Takezou (47)\NFriend of Shibata Shirou
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:17.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for Shibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:23.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's coming over to my place to play mah-jong later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:30.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it doesn't seem like he's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must just be asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, the door's unlocked, TV's on, and he's asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're about to get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, he only ate half of his food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The soup is already cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So is the rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this have been breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a waste of fresh guji...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guji?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's west lake fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you all doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:28.97,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Shibata Kyouko (38)\NWife of Shibata Shirou
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:27.68,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You think you can just go into anyone's home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.97,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm calling the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:36.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:38.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's something in his right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:51.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:12:59.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now let's review your statements...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you four came to visit Shibata Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nand after ringing the doorbell a number of times...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one answered?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came to meet Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nand found the door wasn't locked...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you entered with the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:38.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lastly, there's his wife, Kyouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who\Nmet with Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} moments before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} found Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body in the living room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dead, with his head covered in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that all correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of death is some time in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:02.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And where was his wife at this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:10.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I arranged to meet some friends for golf,\Nwho came around 5:00 A.M in their car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had prepared him breakfast and left before 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, at that time, Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:25.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he came home around 3:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you just say 3:00 A.M.?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's mah-jong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:34.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were playing mah-jong in my room down on the fourth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As she said, we quit around 3:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, there's that newspaper next to his breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know when it was delivered?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's always delivered to the mailbox at around 6:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got up, collected the newspaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, while he was enjoying his breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was attacked and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the most likely scenario, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What tells you he was eating breakfast then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because some of the food on the\Ntable was eaten, and then it went cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, who is responsible for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who killed my husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're still not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, when you entered...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you notice anything peculiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The TV was on that whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The TV was!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why was it off when we arrived!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a little noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:44.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought he was just watching TV and eating breakfast, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was most likely watching that show, "The Hero\NSword Legend," which airs every morning at 8:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:16:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He records it every week and watches it in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There definitely are a lot here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:05.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Check the TV recorder in the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why isn't the LD player here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are LD discs over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's no player.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:21.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, isn't this spot particularly empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only one speaker, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be being repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, actually, my husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That has nothing to do with this case, I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up with your questioning so I can get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:44.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I'll need to confirm it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you get the contact information\Nfor those you were golfing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That goes for you and your mah-jong friends as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They actually picked up the wife at 5:00 A.M.?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:06.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, according to her friends, the time\Nwas reported on the car's radio then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time they brought her home,\Nit was already past 7:00 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,7:00 P.M.?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't we come after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:21.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We went to the newspaper publisher, and they\Nsaid the papers are delivered at 6:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the TV show was recorded, I estimate\Nthat the time of death would probably be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around forty-five minutes prior to 8:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that means the wife couldn't have committed the crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:42.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I must ask Yoshikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're behaving very strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have an alibi for 8:00 A.M. this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I was asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:54.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did anyone see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I live alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember leaving a message after calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said, "It's time to wake up, I'm coming up now."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I killed him, would I have left that message?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you have done it so we wouldn't suspect you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you questioning them, Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way he's the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is someone I can respect: Detective Mouri Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the famous...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Kogoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:36.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's his daughter, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and the\Nkid who lives with them, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:44.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, that beauty beside him is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:59.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to help find an old acquaintance\Nof mine, who happened to be Shibata Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Ikenami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only came to get a thirty year-old\Nphotograph back from Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be the photo in his hand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just saw it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-This...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:26.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would be it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:30.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The photograph I was looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why would Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} be holding this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This photograph is Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s dying message, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be connected to the beautiful Shizuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:55.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, the photograph should be in an album.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must have fallen out or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something under that man's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Thunder God's Door{\i0} is the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The book you mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that would be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:26.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I borrowed it from Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} thirty years ago and\Nleft my photograph inside when I returned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could the criminal be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that an overwhelming coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like how the book and photograph are both on the floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was that strange phone call yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, from Shibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:49.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said, "This is interesting, you should come see."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have been watching a video in this living room then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was talking with someone on the\Nphone while looking for a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, he turned to a certain page of one of\Nthem and said, smiling, "I got it, I got it."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:13.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did your husband put that book?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was on top of that stack of books in front of the bookshelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Yokomizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found blood in the corridor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.13,0:21:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the murder started in this corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. CSI Guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I see that book for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is important evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:45.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, this is a ninja book with a lot of kanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A boy like you can't read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:50.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means you've read the book?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:52.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:57.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, is there a character named "Reiko" in the book?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no character by that name in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:02.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Another one...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:05.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's another lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This woman is a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.09,0:22:11.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But, for what reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:16.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just why is she lying like this?
